<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.2.16">
<l>viṇko ḷamararkaḷ vētaṉai tīramuṉ</l>
<l>maṇkoḷ vacutēvar tammaka ṉāyvantu</l>
<l>tiṇko ḷacurarait tēya vaḷarkiṉṟāṉ</l>
<l>kaṇka ḷiruntavā kāṇīrē kaṉavaḷai yīrvantu kāṇīrē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You with gold bangles, see the quality of the eyes of him who,</l>
<l>Having previously come as the son of Vasudeva, occupying the earth</l>
<l>so that the agony of the immortals in heaven ended,</l>
<l>grows so that the powerful Asuras are weakened. Come and see!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
